WEBVTT

00:10.760 --> 00:13.230
<i>Was it sunny that day?</i>

00:13.550 --> 00:15.050
<i>Was it raining?</i>

00:20.600 --> 00:24.810
<i>My memory is as
fuzzy as the weather.</i>

00:57.800 --> 00:59.260
What? But...

01:19.450 --> 01:23.040
<i>But in that moment... </i>

01:26.620 --> 01:29.170
<i>my heart was filled with blue sky.</i>

01:36.260 --> 01:43.270
<i>[ The Blue Skies at Your Feet ]</i>

02:32.900 --> 02:36.150
Good morning.
You're finally up.

02:38.340 --> 02:39.450
Curry?

02:42.660 --> 02:45.240
Oh, it's recyclable trash day.

02:45.330 --> 02:47.200
Miyu, can you take it out?

02:47.290 --> 02:48.910
What? No way.

02:49.410 --> 02:52.420
Come on, help me out a little.

02:53.850 --> 02:55.380
<i>Especially in the Kanto region,</i>

02:55.380 --> 02:59.610
<i>there is a possibility of strong
rain with localized thunderstorms...</i>

02:59.730 --> 03:01.230
Rain again?

03:01.890 --> 03:04.480
Hurry up and eat it.
Because it won't clean itself up.

03:06.350 --> 03:07.810
Bread would've been better.

03:07.810 --> 03:10.690
It would be a waste. So eat it.

03:12.350 --> 03:16.610
<i>Later in the evening, as cold air
moves south, it will get even colder.</i>

03:16.610 --> 03:18.690
- You're not gonna eat it?
- I don't want it

03:19.570 --> 03:20.640
Hey.

03:22.530 --> 03:24.160
Oh... Miyu!

03:26.400 --> 03:28.290
Geez...

03:30.210 --> 03:32.670
<i>Why won't it keep
together on rainy days?</i>

03:35.040 --> 03:36.200
Miyu.

03:36.670 --> 03:38.840
Your umbrella. Okay.

03:39.270 --> 03:40.710
- Have a nice day.
- Yeah.

03:50.530 --> 03:53.140
Thank you. Have a nice day.

03:54.350 --> 03:56.110
Good morning.

03:57.150 --> 03:59.940
Good morning. Thank you.

03:59.940 --> 04:01.530
Have a nice day.

04:05.410 --> 04:06.820
Whoa, are you okay?

04:06.910 --> 04:08.970
I'm sorry! I'm so sorry.

04:10.250 --> 04:13.210
It's so embarrassing! Stop it!

04:15.080 --> 04:19.330
<i>Curry in the morning, and weather
forecast says it will rain all the time.</i>

04:19.330 --> 04:21.010
I'm so unlucky.

04:22.170 --> 04:23.840
Wow, so cold!

04:29.210 --> 04:30.270
Good morning.

04:31.020 --> 04:32.430
Good morning, Sakiko.

04:32.640 --> 04:33.730
Miyu.

04:34.850 --> 04:35.760
Miyu?

04:36.350 --> 04:36.960
Huh?

04:39.150 --> 04:40.320
You okay?

04:41.650 --> 04:43.490
Huh? Why?

04:44.260 --> 04:48.230
Ah... I was wondering
if you had studied for the test.

04:49.370 --> 04:50.370
Test?

04:50.370 --> 04:53.830
Fourth period,
English test, remember?

04:54.330 --> 04:56.000
Do we have one today?

04:58.550 --> 04:59.630
Ah!

05:00.800 --> 05:02.350
I forgot I'm on class duty, too.

05:02.710 --> 05:03.800
Sorry, I'm going ahead.

05:03.880 --> 05:04.430
Okay.

05:07.760 --> 05:09.510
Here, take this.

05:09.600 --> 05:10.510
Later!

05:21.820 --> 05:23.320
Morning, Yuto.

05:23.400 --> 05:24.740
What's with the mask?

05:29.120 --> 05:29.720
Hey.

05:31.580 --> 05:33.120
What's going on with you two?

05:34.250 --> 05:35.720
Huh? With who?

05:35.960 --> 05:37.210
With Shuya.

05:38.790 --> 05:40.080
What's going on...

05:41.040 --> 05:41.920
Nothing.

05:42.420 --> 05:46.550
Nothing... aren't you guys dating?

05:47.930 --> 05:49.510
I don't know.

05:51.290 --> 05:52.890
What are you saying?

05:53.810 --> 05:56.310
You know, don't you? The rumors.

05:58.900 --> 06:02.320
Are you guys even talking at all?
If you won't tell me, I'll just...

06:02.320 --> 06:05.230
You're so nosy.

06:13.160 --> 06:13.950
Miyu.

06:17.790 --> 06:18.920
Thanks.

06:20.500 --> 06:24.130
But I'm totally fine.

06:31.180 --> 06:32.680
<i>I'm the worst...</i>

06:40.940 --> 06:42.900
Go for it! Go, go!

06:46.650 --> 06:47.900
Yeah!

06:47.990 --> 06:51.110
Nice one! Thank you!

06:51.990 --> 06:53.410
Okay, I'll hand them out.

06:53.410 --> 06:54.660
What...

06:54.740 --> 06:55.910
Ah! Ah!

06:56.410 --> 06:59.330
Score less than 50, and you'll stay
after school to turn in your homework.

06:59.410 --> 07:00.290
What!?

07:00.370 --> 07:02.830
Be quiet. Be quiet.

07:02.830 --> 07:05.250
Okay, put your textbooks away.

07:08.330 --> 07:11.090
Write upper case and
lower case letters clearly.

07:17.770 --> 07:19.020
Shuya, you can do it!

07:30.740 --> 07:32.110
What are you daydreaming about?

07:32.730 --> 07:33.800
Sorry...

07:33.990 --> 07:34.740
Here.

07:37.200 --> 07:39.660
Oh, my God.
Sorry, sorry.

07:40.290 --> 07:42.580
Sorry, sorry.
Thank you.

07:44.710 --> 07:48.920
Shuya, you can do it!
One more!

08:14.350 --> 08:17.120
I heard growling during the test.

08:18.730 --> 08:19.580
Thanks for this.

08:19.580 --> 08:20.470
Did you get it?

08:21.370 --> 08:22.710
I got detention.

08:22.790 --> 08:26.630
What?! Today's the first.
You got a date, remember?

08:27.880 --> 08:31.090
Watch the movie
and tell him what I think...

08:31.800 --> 08:35.800
It's not a date,
it's just a movie night.

08:36.680 --> 08:37.350
Miyu...

08:37.430 --> 08:40.810
I mean, what's the point of
only going to the movies on the first

08:40.810 --> 08:43.600
when we can go anytime
with a student discount?

08:45.390 --> 08:48.110
