08:50.940 --> 08:54.490
Okay, okay.
You're not being honest, Miyu.

08:55.200 --> 08:58.120
Ah... I'm starving.

08:58.520 --> 09:01.830
But it's not that easy
dating someone for two years.

09:02.830 --> 09:03.790
Yes.

09:07.630 --> 09:11.500
I don't know if I'd call it dating...

09:14.770 --> 09:20.300
Miyu, are you still
bothered by the rumors?

09:43.040 --> 09:43.990
