10:04.020 --> 10:05.090
Where?

10:05.090 --> 10:08.270
Well, because everything's handmade.

10:09.020 --> 10:11.320
Egg rolls, can I?

10:13.520 --> 10:14.430
It's yours.

10:14.590 --> 10:16.240
