- Yeah.

10:16.240 --> 10:17.840
Yay!

10:21.370 --> 10:24.290
Mmm... Delicious!

10:25.880 --> 10:27.850
You're exaggerating.

10:27.850 --> 10:30.040
I'll take one!

10:31.040 --> 10:33.250
- It's really good!
- Right!

10:33.250 --> 10:35.000
It's really good.

10:38.260 --> 10:39.090
He's here.

10:42.530 --> 10:43.670
You should go.

10:44.060 --> 10:44.670
Yeah.

10:45.280 --> 10:46.400
I'll be right back.

11:00.490 --> 11:02.240
<i>W-What?</i>

11:03.700 --> 11:04.740
Miyu...

11:15.290 --> 11:16.760
Your hair's a mess.

11:17.550 --> 11:18.760
You overslept?

11:19.720 --> 11:22.050
It won't keep it together on rainy days.

11:24.050 --> 11:24.800
So?

11:25.410 --> 11:27.520
- What is it?
- "What is it?"...

11:28.020 --> 11:30.270
You can go to the
movie today, right?

11:32.980 --> 11:34.670
I'm free today...

11:35.060 --> 11:39.070
What the heck...
It's like I'm inviting you just to kill time.

11:39.280 --> 11:40.490
See you after school.

11:41.650 --> 11:42.930
- Okay.
- Okay.

11:55.790 --> 11:57.290
Do you know what today is?

11:57.920 --> 11:58.750
Movie Day?

12:00.460 --> 12:02.800
Yuto's answer was that
it was my Dad's birthday.

12:05.010 --> 12:07.220
I was thinking of
going to the movies.

12:09.720 --> 12:10.570
With who?

12:11.310 --> 12:11.890
Huh?

12:13.520 --> 12:14.310
The movie...

12:16.270 --> 12:17.610
who are you going with?

12:18.770 --> 12:20.360
I haven't decided yet.

12:20.360 --> 12:23.740
Let's go together.
I was thinking of going too.

12:24.600 --> 12:26.320
- What?
- What are you watching?

12:27.280 --> 12:28.780
- Ah...
- Oh, wait.

12:29.910 --> 12:31.040
Let's say it together.

12:31.790 --> 12:37.000
So, if it's the same movie
we want to see... let's watch it.

12:37.670 --> 12:38.590
What do you think?

12:40.930 --> 12:41.760
Yeah.

12:43.130 --> 12:43.980
Okay.

12:45.410 --> 12:46.120
Okay.

12:47.710 --> 12:48.560
Ready?

12:49.190 --> 12:51.110
- One, two...
- One, two...

12:51.280 --> 12:52.530
"I Want to Eat Your Pancreas".

12:54.070 --> 12:55.320
Why?

12:56.280 --> 12:58.050
You two really are a perfect match.

12:58.170 --> 13:00.530
Why don't you two just go out?

13:00.990 --> 13:01.780
What?

13:02.290 --> 13:03.290
Then...

13:04.930 --> 13:06.090
let's go out?

13:08.150 --> 13:09.040
What...

13:15.120 --> 13:17.720
Congrats, man!

13:17.720 --> 13:19.720
- Way to go, Shuya!
- Congrats!

13:23.470 --> 13:25.180
- Let's take a pic.
- I like that!

13:28.230 --> 13:30.370
Say cheese.

13:38.900 --> 13:40.750
Is it really okay?

14:10.940 --> 14:12.190
Okay, thank you.

14:12.810 --> 14:14.320
See you tomorrow.

14:16.780 --> 14:17.860
Are you done?

14:19.930 --> 14:21.200
Are you okay?

14:22.950 --> 14:24.960
You never got detention before, right?

14:28.000 --> 14:30.080
Okay!

14:30.270 --> 14:34.120
Well, don't be a regular like this guy.

14:34.610 --> 14:35.170
Yes.

14:35.460 --> 14:36.590
What the heck..

14:37.880 --> 14:42.430
- Hey, don't write this in katakana.
- No, no, I didn't.

14:50.070 --> 14:52.870
- Be careful on your way home. Don't detour.
- I won't.

14:54.660 --> 14:56.210
- See you.
- Yes. Bye.

15:00.340 --> 15:01.380
Movie...

15:02.170 --> 15:03.120
you're not going?

15:04.590 --> 15:05.550
I'm going.

15:08.180 --> 15:09.550
I really...

15:10.510 --> 15:12.590
don't get you guys.

15:13.850 --> 15:16.520
I don't even know myself.

15:18.480 --> 15:19.650
- See ya.
- Okay.

15:33.950 --> 15:35.490
Oh, sorry. I'll go on ahead.

15:35.490 --> 15:37.670
- Okay, bye-bye.
- See you tomorrow. Take care.

15:38.290 --> 15:39.030
Miyu!

15:43.550 --> 15:44.460
Hey.

15:45.170 --> 15:46.050
Let's go.

15:46.260 --> 15:47.090
Yeah.

15:49.970 --> 15:51.960
- That's good, right?
- That looks good, right?

15:51.960 --> 15:54.520
- You made a mistake.
- We did?

16:01.400 --> 16:02.400
Hello?

16:04.570 --> 16:07.240
Oh, excuse me for a bit.

16:09.860 --> 16:10.810
Hello?

16:13.660 --> 16:14.700
Really?

16:19.250 --> 16:20.330
Okay.

16:21.210 --> 16:22.590
I'll be on my way.

16:23.210 --> 16:24.380
Thank you.

16:31.760 --> 16:32.800
Sorry, Miyu.

16:32.970 --> 16:34.970
Something urgent came up, so...

16:35.470 --> 16:37.310
I can't watch the movie.

16:39.020 --> 16:40.250
I'm really sorry.

16:42.100 --> 16:43.230
Urgent?

16:48.030 --> 16:49.190
Just a little...

16:52.700 --> 16:53.700
What the...

16:55.330 --> 16:58.000
Sorry. Next week, I promise!

16:59.660 --> 17:00.660
Sorry.

17:04.920 --> 17:05.920
Miyu?

17:09.170 --> 17:10.050
Okay.

17:11.840 --> 17:14.850
No, it's completely alright.

17:18.810 --> 17:19.980
I'm sorry.

17:24.480 --> 17:25.240
I'm sorry.

17:53.220 --> 17:54.010
Go on.

17:55.430 --> 17:56.210
Eat.

18:10.570 --> 18:12.880
Shuya, clear weather suits you.

18:12.990 --> 18:13.640
Huh?

18:15.030 --> 18:17.240
You're like the blue sky.

18:18.370 --> 18:19.040
What?

18:31.550 --> 18:32.550
Miyu.

18:34.220 --> 18:34.970
Huh?

18:35.550 --> 18:36.760
I promise.

18:38.260 --> 18:42.560
First day of every month,
we'll absolutely go to the movies together.

18:42.810 --> 18:43.930
Absolutely?

18:44.020 --> 18:46.060
Yeah, even if we have a fight.

18:46.270 --> 18:46.910
Huh?

18:48.980 --> 18:50.110
No matter what happens.

18:53.440 --> 18:54.030
Okay.

18:55.150 --> 18:56.320
I promise.

18:57.410 --> 18:58.040
Okay.

19:04.790 --> 19:06.090
Let's come here again.

19:17.820 --> 19:21.260
<i>"Starting Tomorrow, My Love For
Her Will Be Rainy" will start soon...</i>

19:21.350 --> 19:24.550
<i>I shouldn't have made that promise.</i>

19:36.750 --> 19:41.930
<i>[ I want to talk to you again.
I'll be waiting for you at the clock tower. ]</i>

20:06.730 --> 20:07.690
I'm sorry.

20:13.440 --> 20:14.440
Miyu!

20:15.320 --> 20:17.490
- Listen to me!
- Enough.

20:19.200 --> 20:20.820
I'm not mad.

20:22.530 --> 20:24.950
If you want to play
with other girls, go ahead.

20:25.870 --> 20:27.580
It's not my business.

20:28.710 --> 20:29.610
What...

20:38.590 --> 20:39.880
I wish...

20:41.590 --> 20:43.470
you would just disappear.

20:45.160 --> 20:45.990
Miyu!

21:28.720 --> 21:29.390
Huh?

21:34.650 --> 21:35.650
A dream?

22:19.270 --> 22:22.490
Good morning. You're finally up.

22:24.790 --> 22:26.370
Why curry again?

22:26.370 --> 22:29.330
Why? Because yesterday's
leftovers would go to waste.

22:29.330 --> 22:30.870
<i>Here is the national weather forecast.</i>

22:30.870 --> 22:34.720
