22:39.380 --> 22:43.010
<i>Low pressure will bring
rain in the evening.</i>

22:44.300 --> 22:45.960
<i>Especially in the Kanto region,</i>

22:45.960 --> 22:49.830
<i>there is a possibility of strong
rain with localized thunderstorms, </i>

22:49.830 --> 22:51.930
<i>so please take precautions.</i>

22:53.060 --> 22:55.510
<i>When you go out, even if it's not raining,</i>

22:55.510 --> 22:57.440
<i>don't forget to bring an umbrella.</i>

22:57.520 --> 23:00.050
Mom, is today the 1st?

23:00.570 --> 23:02.550
That's why it's recyclable trash.

23:02.550 --> 23:06.860
<i>Later in the evening, as cold air
moves south, it will get even colder.</i>

23:12.200 --> 23:13.370
You're not gonna eat it?

23:13.540 --> 23:14.330
I'm good!

23:14.830 --> 23:16.210
Hey!

23:21.380 --> 23:22.210
Miyu?

23:26.340 --> 23:27.590
Geez...

23:27.590 --> 23:30.430
Good morning. Thank you.

23:30.430 --> 23:32.140
Have a nice day.

23:32.140 --> 23:35.530
Good morning. Thank you.

