Good morning. Thank you.

23:39.310 --> 23:40.980
Have a nice day.

23:44.690 --> 23:47.570
- Whoa, are you okay?
- I'm sorry! I'm so sorry.

23:47.650 --> 23:49.030
Ah, it's okay.

23:49.530 --> 23:52.700
It's so embarrassing! Stop it!

23:57.500 --> 23:59.330
Wow, so cold!

24:02.790 --> 24:05.670
What is this? Déjà vu?

24:05.880 --> 24:06.720
Good morning.

24:06.720 --> 24:09.440
- Oh, Sakiko.
- What's wrong?

24:12.640 --> 24:15.220
Shuya's safe, right?

24:15.720 --> 24:16.480
Huh?

24:17.560 --> 24:20.100
No! It's nothing.

24:23.730 --> 24:25.860
Right. Did you study for the test?

24:27.450 --> 24:31.110
Test... English, right?

24:34.120 --> 24:36.660
Here, I'll lend you this.

24:41.710 --> 24:42.630
Miyu?

24:42.630 --> 24:44.800
Oh, sorry, I'm going ahead.

24:44.880 --> 24:45.630
What?

24:52.550 --> 24:54.040
What's wrong with her?

24:55.100 --> 24:56.310
Beats me...

24:56.810 --> 25:01.560
<i>The number you are calling may
not be on, or out of coverage area...</i>

25:23.080 --> 25:24.210
Miyu?

25:24.840 --> 25:26.040
Shuya.

25:27.460 --> 25:29.590
How unusual of you to
come to my classroom.

25:30.470 --> 25:31.800
You're alive...

25:33.800 --> 25:34.720
What?

25:35.130 --> 25:38.100
