25:43.730 --> 25:45.270
Of course not.

25:45.770 --> 25:46.610
You don't...

25:47.230 --> 25:48.280
I do.

25:48.690 --> 25:49.780
Ah, Tomoka.

25:49.950 --> 25:50.830
I'll lend it to you.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.720
